      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Occupational Hazards",
        "Client": "Hapless Trader",
        "Description": "I love when monsters keep destroying\r\nmy carts and my livelihood\u2014said no\r\ntrader ever! First a Lagombi, then a\r\nDiablos, then two Volvidon, and NOW\r\na Rajang and Zinogre! I just want, for\r\nonce, to get from point A to point B\r\nwithout getting beat up by monsters!",
        "Target": "Hunt a Rajang and a Zinogre",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Trop, c\u0027est trop !",
        "Client": "Marchande malchanceuse",
        "Description": "C\u0027est moi ou les monstres ont une\r\nobsession pour ma cargaison ?! Un\r\nLagombi, un Diablos, deux Volvidon\r\net maintenant un Rajang et un\r\nZinogre ?! C\u0027est pas possible d\u0027aller\r\nd\u0027un point A \u00E0 un point B sans me\r\nfaire attaquer, si ?!",
        "Target": "Chasser un Rajang et un Zinogre",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0 ou temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "I rischi del mestiere",
        "Client": "Mercante sfortunata",
        "Description": "Ma s\u00EC, continuate pure a\r\ndistruggermi carro e raccolto!\r\nPrima il Lagombi, poi un\r\nDiablos, poi ben due Volvidon\r\ne ORA un Rajang e uno Zinogre!\r\nPer una volta vorrei spostarmi\r\nsenza interruzioni di mostri!",
        "Target": "Caccia un Rajang e uno Zinogre",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Berufsrisiko",
        "Client": "Gl\u00FCcklose H\u00E4ndlerin",
        "Description": "Ich liebe es, wenn Monster meine\r\nWagen und meine Lebensgrundlage\r\nzerst\u00F6ren \u2013 sprach kein H\u00E4ndler je!\r\nErst ein Lagombi, dann ein Diablos,\r\ndann zwei Volvidon, und JETZT je ein\r\nRajang und Zinogre! Ich will doch nur\r\nunversehrt von A nach B kommen!",
        "Target": "Erjage einen Rajang und einen Zinogre.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "Ojo con los brutos",
        "Client": "Mercader desafortunada",
        "Description": "\u00A1Nada, que los monstruos han\r\ncogido por costumbre atacar\r\nmi carro! El primero fue un\r\nLagombi, despu\u00E9s un Diablos,\r\nluego dos Volvidon, \u00A1y ahora\r\nun Rajang y un Zinogre!\r\n\u00A1No me dejan en paz!",
